Rick McGraw https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rick_McGraw 0 Richard McGraw (March 19, 1955 – November 1, 1985) was an American professional wrestler, best known for his appearances with the World Wrestling Federation (WWF) under the ring name "Quickdraw" Rick McGraw in the late 1970s and early 1980s.
